406
00:33:58,415 --> 00:34:00,974
<i>I mean, we're becoming
a synthesized society...</i>

407
00:34:01,134 --> 00:34:03,662
<i>...in a great, big hurry
to get to the next...</i>

408
00:34:17,173 --> 00:34:20,532
<i>I think it's because we're looking
